# MapTiler API key for Project X map imagery (MapTiler Streets).
#
# Setup:
#   1. Create a free account at https://cloud.maptiler.com/
#   2. Open https://cloud.maptiler.com/account/keys/
#   3. Copy your default API key (or create a new key for Project X)
#   4. Copy this file to maptiler_api_key.txt:
#        cp src/config/maptiler_api_key.txt.example src/config/maptiler_api_key.txt
#   5. Replace this comment block with the key alone (one line, no quotes)
#
# Release builds require a valid key in src/config/maptiler_api_key.txt
# or PROJECTX_MAPTILER_API_KEY set in the environment.
#
# Free tier is sufficient for development. Use a dedicated production key
# for public AppImage/.deb releases.
